lts? \";s:7:\"content\";s:200:\"Yes. Healthy teeth can be moved at any age. Many orthodontic problems can be corrected as easily for adults as for children. Orthodontic forces move teeth in the same way for both adults and children.\";s:1:\"0\";s:0:\"\";s:27:\"flrich1571695228287_content\";s:0:\"\";s:27:\"flrich1571767861419_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:31:\"Do my appliances have to show? \";s:7:\"content\";s:381:\"Many options are available today to minimize the appearance of braces. Todays braces are smaller and sleeker, and some are next-to-invisible.\n\n[Dr.] can advise you about options that will fit your particular needs. You can find more information about types of braces, including Invisalign, here.\n\nThese options allow you to have flexibility and discretion during your treatment.\";s:27:\"flrich1571767877064_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:44:\"Will orthodontic treatment fit my lifestyle?\";s:7:\"content\";s:360:\"You can do almost anything during orthodontic treatment  sing, play a musical instrument, dine out, kiss, and even have your picture taken. Some adjustments may be necessary. But, if youre like the vast majority of adult patients, youll adjust quickly.\n\nNew techniques and materials have made wearing braces more comfortable, and convenient than ever.\";s:27:\"flrich1571767906998_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:42:\"Am I a good fit for orthodontic treatment?\";s:7:\"content\";s:285:\"During your consultation, [Dr.] can determine if you will benefit from treatment.\n\nAfter carefully analyzing the nature of your needed correction, [Dr.] will recommend the best course of treatment for improving your smile, including the different types of braces that are best for you.\";s:27:\"flrich1571767925686_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:68:\"Im missing some teeth. Can orthodontic treatment improve my bite?\";s:7:\"content\";s:208:\"Orthodontic treatment can create or hold space to replace missing teeth.\n\n[Dr.] will work with your dentist or dental specialist. They will provide bridges or implants so that you can achieve the best result.\";s:27:\"flrich1571767944221_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:66:\"Ive been treated for gum disease. Can my teeth be straightened?\";s:7:\"content\";s:279:\"[Dr.] will consult with your dentist and/or periodontist about the health of your gums.\n\nIf you are a candidate for orthodontic treatment, you will continue regular supervision with your dentist and periodontist. In many cases, tooth alignment can improve the health of the gums.\";s:27:\"flrich1571768072399_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:29:\"How much does treatment cost?\";s:7:\"content\";s:400:\"The cost of orthodontic treatment will depend on many factors, including the severity of the problem, its complexity and length of treatment. [Dr.] will be glad to discuss the cost with you before treatment begins.\n\nYou will find that braces are more affordable today than ever. We offer a variety of convenient payment plans, and accept many dental insurance plans that include orthodontic benefits.\";s:27:\"flrich1571768091642_content\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:5:\"label\";s:63:\"Why choose an orthodontist over aligners that come in the mail?\";s:7:\"content\";s:420:\"Orthodontists are dental specialists who diagnose, prevent and treat dental and facial irregularities.\n\n[Dr.] received an additional three full years of specialized education beyond dental school to learn the proper way to align and straighten teeth.\n\nOnly those with this formal education may call themselves orthodontists, and only orthodontists may be members of the American Association of Orthodontists (AAO).\";s:27:\"flrich1571768119433_content\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"collapse\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"open_first\";s:1:\"0\";s:10:\"label_size\";s:5:\"large\";s:12:\"item_spacing\";s:2:\"20\";s:19